attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a wheeled cart. They begin by inspecting the parts and assembling the racks. Next, they align the holes and screw the racks together with black screws, using a screwdriver. They continue by attaching the bars to the base frame and screwing them in with the black screws and screwdriver. Finally, they attach the tray and wheels, tightening everything with a wrench.
